Source: icmp-proxy
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: ICMP Proxy Maintainers <maintainers@icmp-proxy.local>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-python, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3-all, python3-setuptools, python3-wheel
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/hsnprsd/icmp-proxy

Package: icmp-proxy-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: ICMP Proxy shared Python runtime and CLI entry points
 Production-oriented ICMP tunnel proxy runtime shared by client and server
 packages. This package contains the Python modules and command-line entry
 points used by both roles.

Package: icmp-proxy-server
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, icmp-proxy-common (= ${binary:Version}), systemd
Description: ICMP Proxy server systemd service and configuration
 Installs the ICMP Proxy server systemd unit and server environment
 configuration file template under /etc/icmp-proxy.

Package: icmp-proxy-client
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, icmp-proxy-common (= ${binary:Version}), systemd
Description: ICMP Proxy client systemd service and configuration
 Installs the ICMP Proxy client systemd unit and client environment
 configuration file template under /etc/icmp-proxy.
